	\section{\mysidestyle Undergraduate\\Thesis}
	\textbf{Enhanced Index Tracking}\vspace{0.5mm}\\%
	\textsl{Supervisor: Prof. Manoj Thakur, IIT Mandi}\hfill(August, 2015 -- present)\vspace{1mm}\\%
	Index tracking consists of reproducing the performance of a stock-market index by investing in a subset of the stocks included in the index.  All the code for this project is being written in R.
	\begin{list2}
	\item The major problem in the project to be tackled is selecting ’k’ stocks out of available ’n’ stocks.
	\item The \textbf{combinatorial problem} of identifying the assets is solved by heuristic algorithm.
	\item Also, the \textbf{desired return and risk} are to taken care of while selecting the stocks.
	\item Developing a \textbf{back testing framework}  to check the portfolio performance.
	\item Developed a framework which predicts the possibilities of the \textbf{future data}.
	\end{list2}
%________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
% Internships And Projectsjectee
	\section{\mysidestyle Internships And\\Projects}
	
	\textbf{Aadhaar Card OAuth Server}\vspace{0.5mm}\\
	\textsl{Khosla Labs}\hfill(Dec, 2014 -- Feb, 2015)\vspace{1mm}\\
Developed a server which provided \textbf{Sign-in with Aadhaar Card} service. Developed this product using Python, Django Web-framework, and Twitter - Bootstrap.
\begin{list2}
\item Implemented the protocols of \textbf{OAuth2.0}.
\item Retrieved the data from the Aadhaar database, using \textbf{OTP} and/or \textbf{Biometrics}. \item Stored the retrieved data in a local database.
\item Can be used for \textbf{identity verification} and thus can help reduce a lot of frauds.
\end{list2}
	
	
	
	\textbf{Price Comparison Engine}\vspace{0.5mm}\\%
	\textsl{Healthkart.com(Bright Lifecare Pvt Ltd)}\hfill(June, 2014 -- Aug, 2014)\vspace{1mm}\\%
	Built an \textbf{automated system}, which on fed with css selectors of attributes, \textbf{crawls} the websites, \textbf{extracts} the information and \textbf{compares the prices} of similar products on different e-commerce websites.
	 Developed this project using Python, Django Web-framework, Selenium Webdriver, MySQL, CSS and HTML.
	\begin{list2}
	\item \textbf{Tokenised} the sentence and \textbf{matched} the words for identifying the similar products. 
	\item Had also used \textbf{M.R.P. range} as a parameter.
	\item Achieved a high \textbf{accuracy of 90\%}  of matching the products.	
	\end{list2}
	
	\section{\mysidestyle Course\\Projects}
	\textbf{Globalone}\hfill \textsl{Information And Database Systems}\vspace{1.0mm}\\%
	Built an \textbf{interactive organized photo base}, which had features like upload images, \textbf{buy/sell images}, \textbf{tag based autocomplete search}, like or dislike, \textbf{paginated feeds}. Developed this app using Django web-framework, MySQL, HTML5, BootStrap CSS, AJAX. Won the \textbf{first prize} out of \textbf{15 teams}, for this project.\\%
	
	\textbf{Course Registration Portal}\hfill \textsl{Database Practicum}\vspace{1.0mm}\\%
	Devised an app for \textbf{online add/drop courses}, \textbf{grading}, a panel for teachers for \textbf{regulating the course} and automatically generating the \textbf{student ID card}. Used  PHP, MySQL, CSS/HTML, JavaScript and AJAX to develop this app.\\%
	
	
	\textbf{Intelligent Railway Crossing}\hfill \textsl{Design Practicum}\vspace{1.0mm}\\%
	Developed a working prototype which \textbf{closed the gates} of the railway crossing when a train is approached the crossing,  \textbf{opened the gates} when the train has crossed the crossing, gave \textbf{visual and audio warning} before the closing of the gates to the people who are %
	about to cross  the railway line and also issued a warning if any \textbf{person is caught inside}. Used C, Arduino for this project.%

